  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个数字银行系统的整体架构。首先，用户应该能通过Web端和移动端访问系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WebApp",
        "MobileApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个客户端入口。那它们后面是直接连业务服务，还是通过一个统一的入口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WebApp",
        "MobileApp"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要加一个API Gateway作为统一入口，所有请求都先经过它，这样便于做限流和路由。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Web Application和Mobile App都连到API Gateway上了。接下来画后面的服务层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WebApp",
        "MobileApp",
        "API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，核心服务有四个：认证服务、账户服务、交易服务，还有一个通知服务。认证服务必须独立出来，安全要求高。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "AccountService",
        "TransactionService",
        "NotificationService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "四个服务都加上了，API Gateway分别指向它们。认证服务放最上面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "AuthService",
        "AccountService",
        "TransactionService",
        "NotificationService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，顺序不重要，关系对就行。账户服务需要持久化数据，得配个数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AccountService",
        "DB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "账户数据库画好了，圆角矩形表示。交易服务应该也需要自己的存储吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AccountService",
        "DB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，交易数据量很大，而且审计要求严格，单独用一个Transaction Database，和账户数据隔离。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TransactionService",
        "TransactionDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "交易数据库也加上了。通知服务这边怎么处理？直接发邮件短信吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TransactionDB",
        "NotificationService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "通知服务后面要接消息队列，异步处理。高峰期交易量大的话，同步发送会拖垮系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NotificationService",
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "消息队列加上了。那队列后面是消费者处理具体的通知？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，两个Worker：Email Worker处理邮件，SMS Worker处理短信。可以独立扩展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmailWorker",
        "SMSWorker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "都画好了，Email Worker和SMS Worker都从Queue取消息。整个架构看起来完整了，需要加个外框吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue",
        "EmailWorker",
        "SMSWorker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "加一个吧，标注成\"Digital Banking System\"，整体感强一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Digital Banking System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "外框加好了。我检查一遍：Web和Mobile连API Gateway，Gateway后面四个服务，账户和交易各连自己的数据库，通知服务走消息队列到两个Worker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Digital Banking System"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说的认证服务，你画的是AuthService对吧？名字没问题，但我想确认一下位置——它和其他三个服务是平级的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AuthService",
        "AccountService",
        "TransactionService",
        "NotificationService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，四个服务都从API Gateway接收请求，AuthService验证完token之后，其他服务才能处理业务。需要调整层级关系吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "API",
        "AuthService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用，平级是对的。不过我刚注意到，Message Queue的图标你用的是方括号？通常队列用圆括号或者别的形状区分一下？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Queue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
